    <div class="w3-content " style="max-width:1100px ">

        <!-- About Section -->
        <div class="w3-row w3-padding-64 " id="about">
            <div class="w3-col m6 w3-padding-large w3-hide-small ">
                <img src="/images/about-us.jpg " class="w3-round w3-image w3-opacity-min " alt="Table Setting " width="600 " height="750 ">
            </div>

            <div class="w3-col m6 w3-padding-large ">
                <h1 class="w3-center ">About Us</h1><br>
                <h5 class="w3-center ">Pandemic inspired solution</h5>
                <p class="w3-large ">With home deliveries on the rise from the biggest retailers in the country, it's sometimes difficult to find good prices and good ingredients for your meals, as stock for these products is very volatile, especially right now, when the
                    concept of deliveries for every-day produce is still new to a lot of people.</p>
                <p class="w3-large w3-text-grey w3-hide-medium ">With this in mind, we thought of a solution where we make it our duty to find the best produce for healthy, nutritious meals that you, the user, can choose from after selecting a recipe and then select the ingredients that suit you best
                    regarding quality-price wise from one of the stores near you. This makes it simple for the user to create his recipe with hand-picked ingredients, instead of doing the tedious search for below-average ingredients himself.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr>

